title: Diane
subTitle: Steve's lingering physical and emotional scars from the war in Afghanistan plunge him into a soulless routine. He continues his drab existence until the corpse of a beautiful singer, Diane, is dumped in his backyard, shaking him back to reality. Steve takes a photo of her before calling the police, and he becomes obsessed with the dead woman's image. Steve is scrutinized by the police, becoming the prime suspect hassled by Diane's widower, and attacked by self-righteous neighbors.

title: Halloween P... Trap Kill! Kill!
subTitle: When an all-girl rock and roll band is captured by an evil genius, the members must do whatever it takes to stay alive.

title: Nemesis
subTitle: A car accident allows a recovery agent's prisoner, who is a serial killer, to escape into the wilderness, prompting a pursuit.

title: The Shattering
subTitle: Donovan lures several friends into the woods to meet a healer with his cancer-stricken girlfriend. Lucy. As they are hunted by creatures and commandos, the friends realize they were set up to pay for Lucy's cure.

title: Celebrity Crush
subTitle: A deranged fan holds the star of a classic '80s horror movie captive in her home until he falls in love with her.

title: Death's Door
subTitle: A dozen young men and women have a party in a dilapidated mansion. When it's time to go, all of the exits are blocked and the people become trapped.

title: Chopping Block
subTitle: Several corporate guys are laid off and make a plan to kidnap their boss's daughter to ransom her. Their plan takes a bloody turn when they grab her and unwittingly rescue her from a masked psychopath.
